Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.04,0:00:04.48,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Abe no Seimei?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.48,0:00:08.61,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. A powerful onmyoji from the Heian period.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.86,0:00:13.00,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Our family, the Miyako\Nclan, bear his bloodline.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.70,0:00:18.74,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you all about how amazing he was—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.74,0:00:21.28,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, I'm gonna play over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.74,0:00:24.87,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Arata! Arata!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.87,0:00:27.03,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,No, Seimei!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.72,0:00:29.42,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Seimei!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.42,0:00:32.38,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,You are Seimei!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.38,0:00:36.37,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I know it! Your blood smells the same as him!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.37,0:00:38.61,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,No, I—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.29,0:00:42.97,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he's up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.97,0:00:44.73,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.96,0:00:47.98,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Good... morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.07,0:00:52.82,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,You collapsed at the Citizen's Plaza.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.12,0:00:55.82,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess it's understandable.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.82,0:00:58.64,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like you had a busy night.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.40,0:01:00.77,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Hi there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.77,0:01:05.04,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Senda, head of the Shinjuku Ward\N Nocturnal Community Relations Division.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.39,0:01:07.02,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,This is our boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.96,0:01:09.25,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.25,0:01:12.95,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I was planning on making\N introductions tomorrow, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.95,0:01:14.42,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Miyako Arata-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.42,0:01:18.28,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,You've got Ears of Sand, I've heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.02,0:02:52.73,Ep_Title,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,550)}#2 "The White Nekomata of Kagurazaka"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.16,0:02:53.23,Default - Top,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.23,0:02:55.98,sign_4154_27_Storage__1,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Storage #1
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.27,0:02:55.98,sign_4155_28_Nocturnal_Commun,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,1)}Nocturnal Community Relations Division
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.52,0:02:57.63,Default - Top,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,when you've never heard a language before,\N but can still understand it somehow,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.98,0:02:58.74,sign_4220_29_Ears_of_Sand,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Ears of Sand
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.63,0:03:00.50,Default - Top,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,that's called "Ears of Sand!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.50,0:03:04.24,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever had it happen when you \Nwere talking to a foreigner or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.99,0:03:05.88,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.88,0:03:09.33,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,So it doesn't work on human language, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.33,0:03:12.54,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,You understand what the Anothers say, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.54,0:03:14.97,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,That's an amazing new kid we've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.97,0:03:16.27,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.27,0:03:21.13,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Um, how have you dealt with the Anothers\N when you couldn't understand them?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.57,0:03:24.39,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,We've used facial pallor, mannerisms,\N and circumstantial evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.75,0:03:27.14,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Like trying to figure out what\N a cat or dog's thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.76,0:03:32.70,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I've never heard of anyone\N in our line of work
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.70,0:03:36.64,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,in other wards or anywhere in Japan \Nwho could talk to the Anothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.64,0:03:39.03,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Not in the past, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.37,0:03:45.40,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it has something to do with\N them calling you Abe no Seimei?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.12,0:03:48.61,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Wonder what that means.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.78,0:03:52.64,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,My late grandfather once told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.64,0:03:56.67,Flashback,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Our family, the Miyako clan, bear his bloodline.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.67,0:03:59.80,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody believed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.61,0:04:04.31,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you can go for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.31,0:04:06.55,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Your shift's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.55,0:04:08.10,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Goodnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.96,0:04:13.95,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,What a weird night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.95,0:04:17.44,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, what's with that new kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.44,0:04:20.07,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Abe no Seimei, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.48,0:04:23.01,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I thought the exam would get rid of anybody
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.01,0:04:26.07,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,who had relationships or experience like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.07,0:04:28.08,sign_6380_57_Miyako,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Miyako
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.08,0:04:29.33,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.33,0:04:30.88,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,You've come to investigate?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.88,0:04:33.33,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Here's a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.37,0:04:38.54,sign_6555_61_April_6th___Shin,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}April 6th  \NShinjuku Ward, Kagurazaka
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.11,0:04:36.77,Default - Top,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,If we know your connection to Abe no Seimei,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.77,0:04:40.15,Default - Top,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,it'll provide evidence as to whether\N the Ears of Sand are real.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.15,0:04:41.54,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,According to Senda-san, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.85,0:04:44.77,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Evidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.77,0:04:47.59,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Arata, you have guests?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.72,0:04:50.32,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Izumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.74,0:04:52.35,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Co-workers?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.35,0:04:55.11,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for taking care of Arata.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.11,0:04:56.79,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Matsuno Izumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.79,0:04:59.23,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Her parents run that restaurant over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.23,0:05:01.92,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,This is Sakaki-senpai from work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.92,0:05:05.96,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm Seo, his senpai. Seo's in katakana.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.96,0:05:06.74,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.86,0:05:09.74,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Seo-san's the senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.74,0:05:10.97,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.97,0:05:13.28,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Seo got his job the same time\N Section Chief Senda did.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.28,0:05:14.75,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! He did?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.04,0:05:16.87,Default - Top,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Surprised, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.87,0:05:19.99,Default - Top,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Well, anybody would be surprised\N the first time they heard it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.25,0:05:24.01,sign_7631_80_Circular_Notice,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Circular Notice
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.43,0:05:22.44,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you work as a government\N worker on the night shift, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.08,0:05:24.01,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.77,0:05:30.19,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Is it something weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.14,0:05:34.69,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,All my grandfather's things are in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.36,0:05:37.30,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't opened it in a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.27,0:05:42.65,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,When my grandparents were alive\N I used to play in here a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.19,0:05:48.22,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,When they died and my family\N moved in, I stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.70,0:05:53.41,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.72,0:05:55.96,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,My parents said you can take what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.96,0:05:57.68,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,That's nice of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.68,0:05:59.67,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll go check upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.67,0:06:02.38,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we should carry\N out the papers, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.38,0:06:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.42,0:06:10.18,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,What? A cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.56,0:06:18.06,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I-It stood up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.06,0:06:20.65,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Arata!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.05,0:06:24.90,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Arata! Arata!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.90,0:06:29.24,Default - Top,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Arata! Arata! Arata!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.25,0:06:26.43,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.43,0:06:30.06,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,There's an Another down here\N that really likes Miyako.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.16,0:06:32.79,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Two tails...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.79,0:06:33.78,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,A nekomata.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.78,0:06:36.50,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.88,0:06:40.54,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,We always used to play together!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.48,0:06:48.50,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,A white cat with blue eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.24,0:06:50.05,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.05,0:06:51.46,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.46,0:06:54.56,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy to see you again, Arata!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.56,0:06:57.79,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, help me up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.79,0:07:00.56,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, that's a huge nekomata!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.90,0:07:02.98,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,You okay, Miyako?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.44,0:07:04.44,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.83,0:07:08.94,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Arata, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.38,0:07:12.93,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Taking some of the old books and\N stuff in here out and reading them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.93,0:07:13.95,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.23,0:07:20.28,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Your ancestor told me to protect\N what's in the storehouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.28,0:07:21.83,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Ancestors?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.83,0:07:27.17,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Your grandpa's grandpa's\N grandpa... a long way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.17,0:07:28.84,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,My former owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.14,0:07:32.00,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,You've been here that long, Yuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.00,0:07:32.97,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.38,0:07:38.43,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,In the last century or so, you're the\N only one who's been able to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.04,0:07:40.37,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.66,0:07:48.24,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki's been here... all alone...\N protecting the storehouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.78,0:07:58.49,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, why not go with us and watch over them?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.14,0:08:01.82,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,You must be bored in here all the time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.36,0:08:07.67,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,My ancestor wouldn't have wanted\N you to stay in the darkness forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.67,0:08:08.50,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.95,0:08:12.66,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.64,0:08:14.38,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.05,0:08:19.24,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Arata!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.24,0:08:21.73,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.20,0:08:25.27,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I actually... I actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.55,0:08:28.91,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I was so lonely by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.31,0:08:30.81,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Yuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.38,0:08:33.93,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I should've realized sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.94,0:08:38.35,Italics,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Being alone is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.05,0:08:54.59,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Arata, this place is huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.59,0:08:56.55,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like the storehouse at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.01,0:08:58.44,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.44,0:09:00.40,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.14,0:09:02.31,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.85,0:09:06.31,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Miyako Arata, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.31,0:09:08.68,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Arata, you know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.68,0:09:11.32,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Taroubou-sa...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.32,0:09:13.70,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to you? Those bruises...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.70,0:09:15.98,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Well, some stuff happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.98,0:09:16.86,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I got beat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.87,0:09:20.00,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody's against it,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.00,0:09:22.99,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,and my dad and her relatives\N are fighting a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.61,0:09:26.32,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what'll happen now, honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.87,0:09:33.05,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,But you cheered us on, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.60,0:09:37.92,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I really thought you made\N a good couple. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.03,0:09:41.81,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,That made me pretty happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.96,0:09:46.57,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,So... thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.01,0:09:57.79,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.41,0:10:00.70,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Since I get to talk to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:03.18,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I always wanted to!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.52,0:10:06.26,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.83,0:10:09.99,sign_14574_161_Section_Chief___,,0000,0000,0000,,Section Chief    Director
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.32,0:10:09.99,sign_14574_162_Senda,,0000,0000,0000,,Senda
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.01,0:10:23.26,sign_14890_163_Unsolved_Missing,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Unsolved Missing Girl Cases in Tokyo
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.26,0:10:26.27,sign_6555_61_April_6th___Shin,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,May 13th
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.26,0:10:26.27,sign_14944_165_Shinjuku_Imperia,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Shinjuku Imperial Gardens
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.13,0:10:27.94,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,The Anothers are quiet today, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.94,0:10:30.27,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Wish it were always like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.30,0:10:34.74,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.44,0:10:36.53,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,A bird?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.04,0:10:38.86,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's way too big for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.86,0:10:40.53,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,What's on top of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.66,0:10:42.53,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,A person?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.04,0:10:49.54,sign_6555_61_April_6th___Shin,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,May 13th
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.08,0:10:49.54,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.54,0:10:51.43,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.43,0:10:53.42,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody's here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.83,0:10:57.92,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,We have something we need\N to deal with immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.39,0:11:01.17,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,On the Shibuya Ward side of\N the Shinjuku Imperial Gardens,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.17,0:11:03.57,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,somebody witnessed a kisha.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.26,0:11:05.06,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,A kisha?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.06,0:11:15.07,sign_15946_181_Kisha,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Kisha
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.16,0:11:07.85,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,This is a kisha.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.85,0:11:11.28,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,A Chinese Another. A monstrous\N bird that brings disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.28,0:11:14.80,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,It's got ten necks and nine heads,\N so it's also called a nine-headed bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.07,0:11:19.82,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,We've been getting reports of \Nsightings for a while now, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.29,0:11:22.56,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,In January, it was seen in Kyoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.56,0:11:25.58,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,February, Aichi. And then it kept heading east.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.58,0:11:27.55,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Aichi in February?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.55,0:11:29.68,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. The Izuna Incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.68,0:11:32.42,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about? Izuna?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.42,0:11:34.25,sign_16602_191_Aichi_Iizuna_Inc,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Aichi Izuna Incident Video Documentation
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.42,0:11:34.25,sign_16602_192_Aichi_Nocturnal_,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Aichi Nocturnal Community Relations
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.42,0:11:34.27,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,First, look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.27,0:11:38.13,Default - Top,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Senpai, do we have to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.38,0:11:39.12,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,An izuna is a type of weasel Another.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.13,0:11:40.78,Default - Top,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Of course we do, it's our job.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.12,0:11:43.50,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Its tail is made of a metal\N so supple, it's called "living iron."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.50,0:11:45.94,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,It's used in rituals.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.68,0:11:47.86,Italics,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Is that them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.46,0:11:52.98,Italics,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,B-Blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.44,0:11:57.36,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Miyako-kun, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.36,0:12:02.75,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Izuna with their tails cut off were found\N in large numbers in Aichi Prefecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.75,0:12:04.92,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,That's the Izuna Incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.92,0:12:06.62,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.34,0:12:10.37,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,That's the one from before?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.37,0:12:13.11,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.50,0:12:17.25,sign_14944_165_Shinjuku_Imperia,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Shinjuku Imperial Gardens
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.50,0:12:17.25,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Head to the gardens and look\N for traces of the kisha.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.25,0:12:21.53,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,One of its necks is continually\N weeping blood, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.61,0:12:29.31,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Look at all this blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.31,0:12:31.12,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,It's settled, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.12,0:12:33.69,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Is this kisha thing that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.05,0:12:36.84,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,This blood excites Anothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.84,0:12:40.80,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,If a kisha shows up, assume that Another\N incidents are going to more than double.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.80,0:12:42.69,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,That is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.69,0:12:46.05,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,All we can do is be careful and work overtime.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.05,0:12:49.89,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,And pray it goes away as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.89,0:12:52.35,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Could we talk to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.12,0:12:56.00,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I can understand its language.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.00,0:12:59.50,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,So I could tell it that it's causing\N problems and ask it to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.16,0:13:05.24,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, it's an Another. Not a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.24,0:13:10.65,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Talking to them is like talking\N to a typhoon or a volcano.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.65,0:13:11.35,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.35,0:13:13.65,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,It's a side effect of the Ears of Sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.65,0:13:17.31,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,You've got the ability to\N understand them, as well as guts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.31,0:13:20.06,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,It's making them seem closer than they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.06,0:13:25.07,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,What will you do if they\N demand your life in exchange?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.03,0:13:29.95,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Human common sense doesn't work with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.39,0:13:34.08,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,You should learn more about\N the scary parts of Anothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.37,0:13:38.69,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Human common sense\Ndoesn't work with them, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.69,0:13:40.43,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,We can't fly for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.43,0:13:42.29,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys are awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.29,0:13:43.81,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.81,0:13:46.64,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,But we can't fight them, so what do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.64,0:13:48.59,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be attacked by a cat or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.27,0:13:51.57,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,You can't fly?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.04,0:13:53.36,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,He found us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.36,0:13:54.54,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,A human found us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.54,0:13:55.23,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.23,0:13:56.89,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,At a time when we can't fly?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.89,0:13:58.36,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I know this guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.36,0:14:01.23,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,He's the lowest on the totem\N pole at Shinjuku City Hall!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.23,0:14:02.03,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,The lowest?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.03,0:14:02.77,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,The lowest!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.77,0:14:04.06,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.06,0:14:05.62,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Miyako?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.24,0:14:07.11,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Sakaki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.54,0:14:10.53,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,The fairies are upset\N about not being able to fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.53,0:14:12.50,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,We need powder for our wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.50,0:14:17.08,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,But some weird person on\N a big bird took our powder.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.08,0:14:19.29,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,It was a pretty man with long hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.29,0:14:21.04,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,No, a woman! A dark woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.04,0:14:24.02,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,They had the eyes of a beast, shining gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.80,0:14:27.42,sign_20735_254_Storage__1,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Storage #1
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.12,0:14:27.42,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,That's what the fairies said.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.76,0:14:29.92,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,An Another on a kisha, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.92,0:14:32.06,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,That may be the real problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.92,0:14:34.41,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.41,0:14:36.89,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to send you back out\N after you just got back,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.89,0:14:38.83,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,but can you go to Kanoichi Bunko?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.83,0:14:40.07,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,To Kanoichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.07,0:14:43.53,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,They say they need\NMiyako-kun's ears, and fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.53,0:14:46.32,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,It's a good opportunity to \Nmake them owe us one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.61,0:14:48.32,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you the paperwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.97,0:14:51.44,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Kanoichi Bunko Publishing is said to have
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.44,0:14:54.77,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,basically anything you'd want\N to know about eastern magics.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.77,0:15:00.58,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,They're an old clan of onmyoji. They're\N also a family of magical toolmakers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.58,0:15:03.17,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,They fused British magic with Japanese onmyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.17,0:15:05.74,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,They make items used to deal with Anothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.74,0:15:07.84,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Read this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.84,0:15:09.13,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.50,0:15:14.39,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,They seem to have been robbed,\N and an Another saw the whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.39,0:15:18.81,sign_6555_61_April_6th___Shin,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,550)}May 13th\N Chiyoda Ward, Kanoichi Bunko Publishing
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.81,0:15:18.65,Default - Top,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,So they want the Ears of Sand to interpret.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.82,0:15:27.03,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Kanoichi Akane, with the Chiyoda\NWard Nocturnal Community Relations Division.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.03,0:15:32.56,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate you coming all the way to another\N ward to assist with this private matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.56,0:15:35.41,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,No, you do so much for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.34,0:15:38.91,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Miyako Arata-san, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.91,0:15:39.91,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.91,0:15:44.66,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,They're all talking about your\N Ears of Sand in Chiyoda ward, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.07,0:15:47.17,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.17,0:15:49.17,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.51,0:16:06.44,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.71,0:16:08.94,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,The protector goddess of the Kanoichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.69,0:16:12.12,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Is that... a zashiki warashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.12,0:16:13.94,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.30,0:16:16.56,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm amazed she agreed to be your house god.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.56,0:16:19.70,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,You're not supposed to be able\N to bind a zashiki warashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.70,0:16:26.08,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,She allowed us to make her the house god\N in accordance with an ancient contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.42,0:16:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Contract?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.60,0:16:31.98,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Once every ten years, we cut her hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.59,0:16:38.42,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,and offer up a dagger made with\N the Kanoichi's arts as part of a barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.81,0:16:42.60,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,She wishes to seal away\N something beneath it, she says.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.98,0:16:47.72,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,And you want Miyako's help for\N something that has to do with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.72,0:16:48.61,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.61,0:16:51.45,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,If we can't get it back,\Nthe seal will weaken...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.45,0:16:54.80,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,The oni... The oni is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.80,0:16:56.21,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,The bad oni.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.61,0:16:57.66,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Oni?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.51,0:17:01.60,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,You can understand me, Mister?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.60,0:17:03.07,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.20,0:17:07.36,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Arata. Miyako Arata.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.75,0:17:09.16,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.34,0:17:13.16,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Suzuka-chan, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.16,0:17:14.59,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,That's a cute name.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.28,0:17:17.00,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Akane-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.00,0:17:17.75,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.24,0:17:22.14,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,She wants us to call her "Suzu."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.64,0:17:26.66,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,You really can understand her, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.20,0:17:36.14,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Suzu-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.26,0:17:48.07,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,So Suzu-chan, who stole your hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.07,0:17:49.47,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,You'll get it back?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.47,0:17:50.41,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.41,0:17:52.38,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.19,0:17:56.09,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,It was stolen by a beast in human form.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.46,0:17:59.99,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,They're a cheerful, beautiful, black creature...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.99,0:18:02.43,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,But so scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.56,0:18:06.32,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Why did they take your hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.29,0:18:09.44,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.12,0:18:13.57,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,But they said it was almost over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.32,0:18:20.95,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,"A beast in human form," huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.95,0:18:25.70,sign_26397_321_Theft_In_Importe,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Theft{\c&H444744&} In Imported Goods Store
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.28,0:18:24.78,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,It reminds me of what the fairies said..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.70,0:18:31.36,sign_26511_324_Koseido,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Koseidou
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.70,0:18:33.96,sign_26511_325_What_did_the_cul,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,What did the culprit want?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.70,0:18:33.96,sign_26511_326_Theft_In_Importe,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Theft {\c&H2D272F&}In Imported Goods Store
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.56,0:18:29.62,Default - Top,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A thief has broken into a Shinjuku\N Imported Goods Store.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.62,0:18:32.80,Default - Top,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The police are considering it a burglary.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.29,0:18:34.46,Default - Top,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The case was...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.46,0:18:36.56,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that's Koseidou!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.56,0:18:38.43,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,You've heard of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.43,0:18:40.05,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.05,0:18:41.97,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,It's supposed to be an imported goods store.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.28,0:18:46.10,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,But it also gets us the magical stuff we need.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.50,0:18:51.73,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Goat gallstones, mermaid scales,\N burning glass...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.55,0:18:54.59,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Living iron...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.59,0:18:57.03,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy wing powder...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.03,0:18:58.17,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Seo-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.54,0:19:01.17,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Let me think...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.70,0:19:05.87,sign_6555_61_April_6th___Shin,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,1)}May 14th
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.09,0:19:08.29,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.29,0:19:09.50,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.78,0:19:12.09,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.09,0:19:13.45,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Mornin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.04,0:19:15.82,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,You look exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.82,0:19:18.51,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I was checking on something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.51,0:19:21.01,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,You okay to work?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.01,0:19:23.89,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine, I said! We're going to\N Hakoneyama today, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.89,0:19:24.93,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.93,0:19:29.27,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,There've been multiple reports of\N strange fires on top of Mt. Hakoneyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.27,0:19:31.42,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that the fire department's job?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.42,0:19:34.65,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,The fire department and police\N have been out there plenty of times,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.65,0:19:36.27,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,but found nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.27,0:19:38.53,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,So, it's our job now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.53,0:19:44.03,sign_6555_61_April_6th___Shin,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,May 14th
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.92,0:19:47.33,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,This is a pretty famous occult spot, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.33,0:19:48.39,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.39,0:19:52.66,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,It was originally built by the Tokugawa,\N and served as a military base during war.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.66,0:19:55.79,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,There was a hospital\N facility under it, they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.17,0:20:02.46,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Seo, learn anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.46,0:20:05.18,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Some kind of seal or entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.45,0:20:07.43,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Why is this shining?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.93,0:20:08.86,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.56,0:20:16.11,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you touch something\N when you don't know what it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.04,0:20:21.33,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah? I'm kinda busy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.49,0:20:23.57,Italics,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Seo, I just got a call from the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.87,0:20:28.83,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,You were right. It was mermaid scales\N that were stolen from Koseidou.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.45,0:20:30.82,sign_29502_368_Koseidou,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,1)}Koseidou
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.96,0:20:34.41,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Dirt from an old grave...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.41,0:20:35.21,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.08,0:20:40.21,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.08,0:20:42.34,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,You awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.82,0:20:44.77,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.22,0:20:48.20,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.20,0:20:51.72,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Probably inside Hakoneyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.04,0:20:56.10,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,From the height of the ceiling,\N we're pretty far down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.60,0:20:57.63,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.63,0:20:58.55,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.55,0:21:03.99,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Does it not occur to you to check if\N something's safe before you touch it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.64,0:21:06.36,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.24,0:21:09.90,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It's Seimei!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.90,0:21:11.35,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,It's been forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.19,0:21:15.50,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,An Another?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.63,0:21:21.82,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Good timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.82,0:21:24.76,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,My present for you just finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.04,0:21:26.45,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Present?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.45,0:21:27.50,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,What do you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.54,0:21:36.14,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Good, they're moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.10,0:21:39.45,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.22,0:21:44.40,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,People?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.40,0:21:46.36,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,No, those are...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.82,0:21:49.19,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Moving corpses. They're kyoushi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.68,0:21:53.62,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,They're perfect for my reunion with you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.37,0:21:59.54,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Now, have fun, Seimei!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.34,0:23:35.75,Next_Ep_Title,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1)}#3 "The Trickster with Amber Eyes"
